{"tid":2438380,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大救生艇│大專生人才開放工作簽證計畫討論區(1) 16年畢業生最後召集","createTime":"2021-03-08T12:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T23:29:50.000Z","uid":91244,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"43eece7f4dae8d9f41e75a27cc0b523cf3ee516d","tid":2438380,"uid":91244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:39:09.000Z","msg":"加拿大於上年宣布港人移居<span class=\"red\">救生艇計劃（Lifeboat Scheme）</span>。而第一輪「<span class=\"gold\">開放工作簽證申請</span>」已經於今年2月8日開始接受申請，允許5年之內在大專畢業、或者是有大專以上學位的年輕人，可以取得最多三年的 「開放工作簽證」 （Open Work Permit），<span class=\"gold\">最快一年可申請永居。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\">大專移民谷</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/IfOKhh-NkIuGRs8H\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FIfOKhh-NkIuGRs8H&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv4TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=2b0b071f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/IfOKhh-NkIuGRs8H</a><br />\n群組內設懶人包，解答到大部份常見問題<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"orange\">申請資格:</span></span><br />\n1. 需持香港特別行政區護照或BNO<br />\n2. 年滿18 歲或以上<br />\n3. 最近5年內完成2年或以上大專課程<br />\n<br />\n滿足以上條件，即可申請加拿大3年工作簽證，而符合最低語言及學歷等要求，並於加拿大有 1 年工作經驗便可申請永久居留，有關永久居留之詳情於稍後時間公布。<br />\n<br />\nPS: 受限於疫情下的額外入境措施，海外申請人現時仍要先獲當地工作職位始能前往當地。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\">申請截止日期:</span></span><br />\n計劃將於2023年2月7日結束，請盡早申請"},{"pid":"f805c1c4e5bf161be8ff1cc157f2adae0cc6329b","tid":2438380,"uid":144718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:39:32.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"8f0bc8c329fc9368e1cdfcf307c0e5fa15a6c634","tid":2438380,"uid":129042,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:41:47.000Z","msg":"傻鳩先去加拿大<br />\n緊係去英國"},{"pid":"8c96947028ba8802cd22db9765c2e59144e9dcff","tid":2438380,"uid":35408,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"8f0bc8c329fc9368e1cdfcf307c0e5fa15a6c634","tid":2438380,"uid":129042,"like":5,"dislike"